2016-03-31 Release 0.2.5
- Feature: Support logrotate through `logrotate_on` #50
- Feature: Support watches definition in Hiera #59
- Bugfix: Don't use root if we launch through Upstart or Systemd #51 #60
- Bugfix: Allow both or neither of `template` and `source` to be set #52
- Bugfix: Anchors to improve dependency resolution #62 #63
- Bugfix: All `consul_template` releases are now zipfiles - remove `strip` arg #65

